*              |            | TRANSPORT REQUESTS                       *
************************************************************************
* CANOCAR      | 12.08.2022 | 12891      : BRF+ comsumption from RAP   *
*              |            | DS4K926772                               *
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*

    APPEND 'AUART' TO et_requested_orig_elements.

  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.